Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.99,0:01:41.24,Title2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs58\fad(450,400)\blur6\pos(1112,185)}暴風雨的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}里克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}醒醒呀 里克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}艾雅莉...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已經到起床時間了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的 比以前還來得早一些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒什麼 發生什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}馬黛拉說今天一定會非常的忙 讓大家一起來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然還覺得有點睏 一起去吧 吶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:45.81,Title2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs58\fad(450,0)\blur6\pos(626,625)}— 馬黛拉麵包坊 —
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:51.81,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48\blur12\pos(526,185)}『今天在魯克魯．麵包坊營業
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:51.81,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48\blur12\pos(618,235)}前來購買的顧客請至魯克魯．麵包坊』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:54.82,Title2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\fad(450,0)\blur6\pos(540,625)}— 麵包坊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:54.82,Title2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\fad(450,0)\blur6\pos(734,623)}魯.克魯 —
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有希爾芙森林的{\fs48\b\fn華康海報體W9}菈娜{\r}{\blur5}帶來的口信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說這次的暴風雨不同已往
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是我們能做的也只有做麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}暴風雨的時候 大家都會在家裡吃飯的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼就是麵包店最繁忙的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已經很熟練了呢 里克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有點資深師傅的樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和以前只顧眼前的工作光看著食譜相比
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}進步很多囉~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呼咧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦？？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太過於用力了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等等烤的時候會起褶皺的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 這樣啊....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哼...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊啊~ 被罵了吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘻嘻...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然還是比不過馬黛拉的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來~ 只差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一起加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早安~歡迎光臨~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多謝惠顧~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個... 暴風雨要鄰近了好像很強烈的樣子 請當心點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊... 真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}以前從沒發生過的強烈暴風雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}當心點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}馬黛拉都這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你告訴我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒關係~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}馬黛拉都這麼說了 肯定不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是當然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真不愧是馬黛拉 被大家信任著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}路上小心~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 明天也拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請小心暴風雨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}艾雅莉姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家 都做好小孩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來~ 早晨的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天是葡萄麵包！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝~ 謝謝~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吶 姐姐 今天早上開始風就好大 小孩子都有點害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吶 大家 那個啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}暴風雨將要鄰近了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}暴風雨？ 不會有事的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好害怕哦 姐姐~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}待在屋子裡不出來的話就沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是應該是很大的風和雨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}絕對不能到教會外面去唷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好嗎~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}Hi~！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很好~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}城裡發出的告示啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是「暴風雨要鄰近了好像很強烈的樣子 大家請小心點」的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好~ 可以了哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好了 今天早點回去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}肯定是強烈的暴風雨啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就這麼做吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}潮水退下去不少了啊 會有大波瀾了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 我去將網收好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總之小心點會比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}終於快到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}上夜班的真倒霉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我回家還有小花熱騰騰的雜燴湯等著我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}切... 只會拿老婆的菜來放閃光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}顆顆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天很早就起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好睏...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吶 里克 艾雅莉回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已經到晚上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我去找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}亞蜜露接下來拜託你囉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我瞭解了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}反正要去順便帶上剩下的麵包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我去準備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}阿啦~ 麵包師父啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗨？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天是你來賣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘿 嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼給我一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:41.77,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48\blur12\pos(366,129)}『強烈的暴風雨鄰近了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:41.77,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48\blur12\pos(486,179)}請做好防備工作』
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an8}這樣的 媽媽她...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}通常都是這個時間回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天好像會晚點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼在你媽媽來之前我陪著你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呃哈...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯哼哼~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:07:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要吃嗎~？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈... 好美味的樣子~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呃... 但是現在身上沒帶錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒關係 一個人等媽媽的獎勵~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈...  謝謝~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是好香的味道啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真好吃啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}艾雅莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}里克！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真抱歉 這麼晚還沒回家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你沒發生事情就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個孩子是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一直在這等媽媽來接她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘿... 是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘻嘻...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}媽媽的工作是什麼呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在城外的蘋果園裡工作哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}差不多要到蘋果成熟的時候了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯... 但是媽媽說強烈的暴風雨要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為了保護蘋果樹今天會很辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很不容易種出來的蘋果 因為暴風雨而毀了 會很失望的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是要如何保護好蘋果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈~ 我知道的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼做的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}用很大的架子圍住的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}圍住蘋果樹？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的 在蘋果園周圍搭起很大的架子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯嗯~ 然後呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後呢~ 再掛上布呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能把房子都遮住的那種哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是很大的布呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯~ 固定成就算是暴風也吹不倒的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是把蘋果園都遮起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈... 聽起來很辛苦的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}趁雨還沒下大之前回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈！ 是媽媽呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了 那麼小心點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩 姐姐 謝謝你的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大哥哥~ 謝謝你一起陪我等媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:09:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}將這個拿給媽媽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對媽媽說句辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈~ 謝謝~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}bye~ bye~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們也回去吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊~ 今天真是好忙啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩 比以往來了更多的客人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個... 昰那孩子的媽媽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像是的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是不是蘋果園的工作還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦 那麼... 那孩子一個人在家？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}或許是這樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}艾雅莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}爐火還沒熄哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不好意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不好意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是我 聽得出來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姊姊！~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事吧~?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從魯克魯送來的麵包~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:11:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是哥哥幫你做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為了讓你不孤單的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在媽媽回來之前能堅持下去嗎~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯！~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘻...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}辛苦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}馬黛拉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}擦肩而過 在雨下大之前回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦？ 但是里克怎麼辦...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道是在等我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼今天的工作就完美結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}累翻天了啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}比起以往還要更早起來工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉呢 里克是最累的一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有這樣的事啊 但是好想快點睡一覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能借我一下雨傘嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這下… 沒辦法回去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再一個？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}里克來到這個島的時候也是這樣的暴風雨日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}最初還在想接下來會怎麼樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能一起工作真的是太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}麵包也做的十分的熟練了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是馬黛拉教的好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦 那我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦？ 啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩 亞蜜露的... 評價也很好呢 麵包...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}當然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼覺得是在敷衍我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊哼哼~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘻...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}製作者和教導的人 或許是不同的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 是這個意思啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩 不止這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}亞蜜露不是喜歡照顧人的類型嗎~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是這樣嘛！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}里克要失敗的時候 馬上就跑去幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這... 這麼說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}妮莉絲也在里克想幫忙收銀的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}急著讓他去休息吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是因為找錯錢就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊~ 妮莉絲最喜歡錢了呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才．不．是．呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我只是擔心里克...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘻...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈哈...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呃 什麼嘛... 真是的~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吶 想聽一下我送護身符給小女孩的事情嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想聽~ 想聽~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}噓~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後呢~ 然後呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個小女孩的媽媽在蘋果園工作的...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}出發~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這麼早就來 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早安~ 哥哥~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}護身符麵包真是謝謝啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天的暴風雨在家沒嚇到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯~ 沒關係的~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐！~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早安啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨晚真了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘻嘻...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}託護身符麵包的關係唷~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的？ 太好了！~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天真的太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女兒讓你們擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 沒這樣的事的~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是你們通知鎮裡的人強烈的暴風雨鄰近了的這件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘿 嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 做為昨天的謝禮 不介意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}非常感謝妳~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是多虧了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}向大家傳達了暴風雨鄰近的這件事 我們果園才平安無事的蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天的特色菜單決定了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}做些什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}用這個做好吃蘋果餡餅吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.84,0:17:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:17:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯！~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早安呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}幸福的麵包做好了哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}歡迎來到魯克魯~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天就是幫大忙了 通知我們暴風雨鄰近了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}家裡沒發生事情吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多虧了你們預防好了呢 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吃了你們的麵包心裡也暖呼呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們的孩子昨天也沒留下什麼恐怖的回憶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們家也是 3Q啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an8}得救了啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an8}謝謝~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an8}真的很感謝...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們才是~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝大家了~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣啊 被大家感謝了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那可真是太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯~ 呵呵~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是如果收到了很多人的感謝的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可不能在自己手上停下感謝的播種啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}感謝的種子應該已經蔓延開了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請借一下麵包爐！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂~ 哥哥 好不容易人家幫你送過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你好~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你好！~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}特地讓你出來 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們來送麵包的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈！ 哥哥 有果仁麵包唷~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯~~ 好香的味道呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哥哥 太好了呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼做這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:19:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}印象中沒拜託過你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}讓鎮裡的人知道暴風雨鄰近了從而能防備的就是{\fs48\b\fn華康海報體W9}菈娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是我們卻被大家感謝著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以這是我們對你們的感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}本來就是哥哥告訴我的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以哥哥也一定要收下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來~ 果仁麵包~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯嗚~ 好美味呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哼...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總之還算可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝x3~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哎~ 嘻嘻~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是不坦率呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}合不合菈娜的口味呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:20:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 足夠了...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈... 不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}簡直最棒了啊！ 這個~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘻...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an8}接近島的迷之大型船
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an8}為了不讓他找到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an8}全鎮進行熄燈活動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an8}能這麼順利的進行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an8}下回 也為了做出幸福的麵包！
